lass=\"popover\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"popover__content\"\u003e\u003cul class=\"popover__list\"\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/collections/trending-themes\" class=\"marketing-nav__item marketing-nav__item--child\" itemprop=\"name\" data-ga-event=\"Main Nav\" data-ga-action=\"Clicked\" data-ga-label=\"trending-themes\"\u003eTrending this week \u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/collections/product-recommendations\" class=\"marketing-nav__item marketing-nav__item--child\" itemprop=\"name\" data-ga-e\n...........\n+++\n\nFinally, when user visits the homepage: https://themes.shopify.com, so many images, css, link will not be loaded (Because the port :1337 which appended themes.shopify.com:1337 is not opened\nPlease see the attached image for details.\n\ncheers,\n~g4mm4\nReferences:\nhttps://portswigger.net/research/web-cache-entanglement\nDenial of Services\n\n## Impact\n\nDenial of Services","bounty_amount":"2900.0","formatted_bounty":"$2,900","weakness":{"id":48,"name":"Uncontrolled Resource Consumption"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":1185403,"file_name":"PoC-Host-Header-cache-poisoned-DoS.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/k7gjzfubyrizpmk5qw7dq9rbg3mo?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22PoC-Host-Header-cache-poisoned-DoS.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27PoC-Host-Header-cache-poisoned-DoS.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQ6Q7LE23M%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T082513Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQD89%2F02d1cHdrUV1MbFWOJ5ke6Za7uczudQw2c%2FrnZD0gIhAPVin0%2FV70VgUHMUtzzC%2BODrx7rPLYKCTP3Uhk5Uv8j5KrsFCPD%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQAxoMMDEzNjE5Mjc0ODQ5IgzdJ28GgBZebhpSG%2FsqjwU4KEexjUBaU8MWvfVk0Bjliok%2FpP3sVUEAFGQRQ9Foo6R4d73MTb